Atomic Heart is a new adventure role-playing action game that shows you the world, which takes place in an alternative Soviet Union of 1955. Scientist Dmitry Sechenov, the head of Facility 3826 (the scientific research hub built to produce robots), created a wireless, networked artificial intelligence that linked his robots together for greater efficiency. It was called “Kollektiv 1.0”. Then, Dr. Sechenov developed the THOUGHT neuroconnector, a device that allows humans to remotely interface with robots, and wanted to release it alongside “Kollektiv 2.0”. However, the launch of “Kollektiv 2.0” was sabotaged, and the scientific research hub was plunged into chaos. The Facility’s robots have become hostile and massacred most of the human personnel.

We offer you to buy Atomic Heart key, so you can find out what happened and why the robots became hostile. You will take on the role of an experienced soldier and a veteran of numerous battles, who was invited to assist in the rollout of “Kollektiv 2.0”, but after the launch is tasked to investigate the incident and restore the neural network. During the mission, you will explore every nook and cranny of the research hub and visit scientific complexes and mysterious laboratories. You will also wander on the surface and explore the civilian infrastructure. You won’t travel alone: the artificial intelligence built into a special glove will help you. You can talk to it and get important information about the characters and the secrets of the facility. The Polymer Glove grants you powers such as energy shields, telekinesis, freezing, and electricity to defeat your enemies.
